feed.title: Suntec Temp
feed.description:
Outdoor temp at Suntec weather station

My Davis VantagePro2 weather station is connected to a  Hautespot IP (http://www.ambientweather.com/haipandwiwes.html) to send weather data to Weather Underground.   Weather Underground makes the data (XML) available with an API (http://www.wunderground.com/weather/api).  Then use the website http://xml2csv.appspot.com/ to convert the XML to CSV.  I only want one value: temp_f.  I put wunderground XML URL in the URL field in xml2csv, then click browse button, then click temp_f link.  Then right-click permalink (no header) and copy URL.  Then paste this URL to  pachube - "pull data for you" field.  Then add datastream 0.
